<Layout title="巡礼ルート - 52kmの聖なる巡礼 | カイラス2026" description="カイラス山の52km外側コーラ完全ガイド：1日、2日間、3日間の巡礼プラン。13ヶ所の補給拠点、標高変化、重要アドバイス付き。タルチェン出発、5648mドルマラ峠越え。">

  <!-- Hero Section with full-width photo overlay -->
  <section class="relative bg-kailash-dark">
    <!-- Full-width photo -->
    <div class="relative w-full h-[45vh] lg:h-[55vh]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/kailash-yaks.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-transparent to-kailash-dark"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content below photo -->
    <div class="relative -mt-20 z-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          巡礼ルート
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/60 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          52km、3日間、信仰から出発し、魂へと帰る
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 mt-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-gold">52 km</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">総距離</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-gold">5,648 m</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">最高地点</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-gold">3日間</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">標準日程</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <section class="bg-kailash-dark py-8 border-t border-white/10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-gold">52 km</p>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">総距離</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-gold">5,648 m</p>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">最高地点</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-gold">4,600 m</p>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">基準標高</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-gold">13</p>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">補給拠点</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Route Overview -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4">ルート概要</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">標高変化と主要中継地点</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Route Map -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">カイラス巡礼ルートマップ</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">52kmの聖なる道 — 聖山を一周する巡礼</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/kailash-trek-map.webp" alt="カイラス巡礼ルートマップ" class="w-full block" style="min-height: 400px;" loading="eager" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
          <div style="display: none;" class="p-8 text-center text-gray-500">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 text-kailash-gold/50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            <p>マップを読み込み中...</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Route Scenery -->
      <div class="mt-16 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4">ルートの風景</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">歩みで信仰を測り、目で聖なる山を仰ぐ</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/route-map-1.webp" alt="ドルマラ峠の祈福の旗" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>画像読み込み失敗</span>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent p-4">
                <p class="text-white font-semibold">ドルマラ峠 · 祈福の旗</p>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">Drolma La Pass · Prayer Flags</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4">
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">標高5648メートルの最高地点、巡礼者たちが祝福を祈りここに経旗を掲げます。色とりどりのルンタが風の中でマントラを唱えます。</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/route-map-2.webp" alt="カイラス山と馬隊の休息" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>画像読み込み失敗</span>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent p-4">
                <p class="text-white font-semibold">聖山の眺望 · 馬隊の休息</p>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">Mount Kailash View · Horse Caravan Rest</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4">
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">雲に包まれたカイラス山、渓谷で休息する馬のキャラバン、遠くに仮設キャンプの煙が立ち上る。</p>
            </div>
